Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150525,153278}What?\NMaya's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153278,154613}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154613,157824}The audition is tomorrow,\Nbut I still haven't heard from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159493,161495}Oh, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:43.28,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:160911,163288}{\fad(1500,0)}Tōtō University Medical Center
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163747,165707}We haven't heard from her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165707,169628}Is that right?\NHaven't heard from her…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173340,174966}Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174966,176885}Go pick her up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176885,178637}Otherwise, she might not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200242,201702}Here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203370,204870}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216340,218009}Wh-What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218009,219386}She's playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221430,225350}Babies often play like that,\Nsmiling like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234234,236319}She's totally become Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236319,239281}She even forgot the day\Nof her important audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243201,245161}Here, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256465,257507}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260385,262763}Rei, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262763,265265}Maya, your audition is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265265,268018}Oh, it has been that long…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271938,274441}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274441,276318}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276318,277778}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277778,280113}Mr., Mrs., I'll see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280113,282032}She seems just like an ordinary girl like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282032,283074}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284075,286203}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.25,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:290290,293251}"The Miracle Worker" Audition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296838,301676}We will now start the audition\Nfor the role of Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302719,304638}Here, we have the five candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305972,309226}What's wrong with that Kitajima Maya girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309226,311436}She has scratches all over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311436,315065}Yeah, she looks like she just got out\Nof volleyball practice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315065,319319}The six judges are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319319,326116}Mrs. Himekawa Utako, who has not arrived yet\Ndue to her delayed flight, will be joining us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331122,335085}Mrs. Himekawa is the mother\Nof Ms. Himekawa Ayumi, one of our candidates…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335085,337963}…but the selection process will be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337963,340090}It's easy to say "fair,"\Nbut, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340090,344261}Yeah, of course you'd have special feelings\Nfor your own daughter, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344636,347097}Now, let's begin the first audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347097,349975}Candidates, please change into your costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349975,351268}This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355981,358650}Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361820,365073}It's been a month since they have parted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365073,367284}An emotional moment\Nfor mother and daughter to rejoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380005,382299}Oh, they just passed each other by\Nwithout even looking at one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382299,385051}They'll remain as strangers\Nas long as the audition continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385051,386385}What a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388722,391141}I know she has a strict eye for Ayumi's act…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391141,395645}…but I will do my best on my terms,\Non behalf of Mr. Purple Rose, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399024,401984}The audition has started downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410744,414122}Candidate number one,\NMs. Shiratori Reina, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414122,415332}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415332,416333}Shiratori Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416333,416917}Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416917,418209}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419628,420794}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422421,427510}The first audition is to play as Helen.\NPlease start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427510,428511}As Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431765,434684}I know, she liked dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444611,446613}Candidate number two,\NMs. Hayakawa Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446613,447280}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452911,454996}Okay, I'll use the blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475976,479688}Kanaya Emi's play\Nis different from the first two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479688,482440}She's about to use all the toys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482440,486653}It's rare to see an act like hers\Nthat doesn't bore the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486653,489531}Very dynamic,\Nand it will be great on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:17.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493535,497831}Maya, I'm sure she feels insecure\Ngoing up against Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501543,503420}Candidate number four,\NHimekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506840,509009}Play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522772,524691}W-What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524691,527485}She seems to be\Nplaying with her nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534367,536745}I wonder how long\Nshe'll be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536745,537454}I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537454,538455}Hasegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538455,539414}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540957,542834}That ball, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542834,543960}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543960,545837}It's okay.\NJust do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562771,564189}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582082,585418}She had her eyes wide open\Nwithout even moving her eyes off the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585418,588463}I'm sure that's what Helen would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600141,604604}I'm looking forward to seeing what kind\Nof play the last candidate can show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604604,606606}Play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613279,614488}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614488,618118}What's going on with her\Nand Himekawa Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619369,620495}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630213,632423}She's fallen asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632423,633633}That's unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633633,636553}What do you think this audition is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636553,639514}Hey, you!\NHey—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640723,643601}We told you to play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643601,645103}Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648815,651442}Hey, you!\NWhat…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657365,658449}Hey, just…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658449,660493}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660493,665373}Just look at her.\NHer hands, her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665373,668835}She's playing, as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668835,672130}She's enjoying tearing the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672130,676759}An ordinary person would come\Nin here and play with the toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676759,678386}That is common sense, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678386,681472}But, if the real Helen were here,\Nwhat would she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681472,683641}Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683641,686060}She wouldn't notice that\Nthe toys were here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:36.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690564,696529}This girl and Himekawa Ayumi\Ndefinitely possess extraordinary talent.
Comment: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:45.70,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:705705,705705}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:49.29,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:709292,709292}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:52.21,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:712212,712212}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720678,725183}The meeting is about to start\Nin the third conference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729103,732232}They reported the results\Nfrom the second audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732232,734484}It's the simulated acting\Non the actual stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734484,739572}Shiratori Reina and Hayakawa Akiko\Nhave equal chances of passing or failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741991,748456}Kitajima Maya acted wildly,\Nbut the judges didn't like it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750208,754003}At this point, Kanaya Emi,\Nwith her dynamic acting…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754003,758591}…and Himekawa Ayumi, who showed\Nimpressive emotion, are leading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759342,761552}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:52.14,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:768434,772146}The audition came to the last test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777443,779779}The judges will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779779,782699}Please wait here as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782699,784951}This is the last test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785451,789706}I wonder if anyone\Ncan pass this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789706,793042}If anyone does,\Nthen she's the real Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793042,800300}If not, let's vote for one of these two.\NHimekawa Ayumi or Kanaya Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:32.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806848,812312}If I don't get this role,\Nthen Miss Tsukikage will expel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:38.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814063,818443}No, right now, let's focus only on being Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:43.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818443,823406}It might be my last chance to be Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823406,825199}I am Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826367,828244}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:52.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828244,832707}I know she will meet\Nmy expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.66,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:832707,834667}Bidoro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837420,838588}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843509,844594}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.01,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:850558,852017}Alarm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862195,864405}This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864405,866449}Unbelievable.\NNo way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888638,889472}It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889472,890723}I wonder what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894519,895686}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897438,899023}The last test is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:14:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899023,899439}What!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899439,901609}Over?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902402,904737}The alarm was the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905363,907949}You were told at the beginning\Nto wait as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909367,917917}Given that, though, it is human nature\Nto react to something like the loud alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918291,920878}The ones who didn't react are\Neither the real Helen…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920878,923923}…or the ones who can play the real Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925216,928678}A long time ago, at the audition\Nfor "The Miracle Worker" in America…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928678,932682}…there was one girl\Nwho didn't react to a loud noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932682,941566}The girl later became known as Patty Duke (Atson),\Nwho won an Academy Award at the age of 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941566,944527}Now, we have two Pattys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945820,949240}I see. I didn't even notice\Nthat it was the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949240,951033}Didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951033,954370}Yes. I was thinking this might be\Nthe last time I can play Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954370,959041}Then I started to forget that I was Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959040,963129}I knew the alarm was going off,\Nbut I didn't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963129,964797}This girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964797,966799}What about you, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968175,970094}I just played the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970094,972096}You told me to wait as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973014,976058}Then what if it was a real emergency alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976058,978895}I wouldn't have stopped\Nuntil I was told to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980229,983900}Great work, Ms. Himekawa.\NExcellent acting spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983900,986694}No wonder the critics call you a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988362,993950}Judges, may I please be excused now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993950,995453}Ms. Kanaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995453,998498}There's no need for me\Nto be here anymore now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998498,1000666}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006923,1011636}Kanaya Emi, I would like to cast her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012678,1015723}No, I would like to lobby for\NHimekawa Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015723,1017725}Just think about\Nthe acting audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018392,1021812}Kitajima Maya's simple acting\Nis no comparison to hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021812,1023773}Yes, I would agree with him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023773,1028027}Imagine them appearing on stage\Nas a co-star mother and daughter.{NOTE:姫川亜弓のネームバリュー 母親のうたこさんとの共演}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028027,1030404}It will bring merit to the theater\Njust for that factor alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030404,1031739}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031739,1037370}I don't mean to interrupt, but we shouldn't\Nhave had an audition if you use those criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037370,1038579}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038579,1041582}The purpose of the audition\Nis to judge solely by acting…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041582,1043626}Argue all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043626,1046170}The executive director\Nand the manager are on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046170,1049048}Besides, we have Himekawa Utako and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:33.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049048,1053844}We'll chose Himekawa Ayumi\Nfor Helen by 4 to 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054136,1058266}I was very intrigued by Kitajima Maya's acting for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058266,1059517}So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059517,1064814}I have high expectations that she will play Helen\Nas she has never been played before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064814,1066983}We can't run a business on just expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066983,1067900}But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067900,1068859}Enough said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068859,1071571}I say we put it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071571,1074323}Let's be democratic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078327,1081038}I'm scared. They haven't\Nmade up their minds yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:06.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081038,1086877}Help me, Mother, Rei,\Neveryone… Sakurakōji…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086877,1088004}Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:13.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089922,1093801}Why is it taking so long?\NWhat's going on inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:18.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093801,1098931}I, Himekawa Ayumi,\Nhave so much insecurity and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101601,1103185}This girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:24.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103185,1104353}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104353,1106814}It's because Maya's my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:29.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106814,1109734}She's making me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112153,1115615}I see, they will vote to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.90,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1115448,1117908}Meeting in session
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115615,1118534}It must be tough for Himekawa Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118534,1122120}She's torn between the love of a mother\Nand her pride as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139889,1141974}I will read the votes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147146,1148314}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150483,1151734}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153778,1154904}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156530,1157531}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159825,1161369}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162870,1164163}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172713,1174256}Three to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174256,1177385}The last vote will decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178928,1180846}Them, I will read the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185267,1187269}Hmm…\NT-This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188688,1189397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189397,1191315}Whose name is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202410,1203703}Both names…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205620,1207289}Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207289,1208749}It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209834,1210960}Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212962,1217341}I chose as the actress\Nwho will play Annie Sullivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217341,1222471}I'm sure Himekawa Ayumi\Nwill play the perfect the perfect Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222471,1228602}However, Kitajima Maya might play Helen\Nas she has never been portrayed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228602,1232314}I couldn't discard either from my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239572,1243826}I hereby announce the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243826,1247163}Helen Keller will be played by…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247163,1248748}…Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255129,1257214}And, also, by Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265765,1268768}We decided to double cast them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269852,1271270}Double cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:16.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275316,1276817}With Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278486,1279528}With this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281405,1287995}They will take turns each day to play Helen Keller\Nwith Annie Sullivan, played by Himekawa Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287995,1294084}By the way, this play, "The Miracle Worker," might\Nbe nominated for acting awards by the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294794,1297463}Now, please greet each other\Nin the spirit of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:49.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308641,1309975}Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313020,1314355}I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322238,1323823}I will play Helen with Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:07.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324657,1327618}Under Director Onodera…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327618,1330788}…and with her mother as Annie Sullivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331664,1334250}I wonder if I can go on, as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339630,1341674}So, the decision has been made.
Comment: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:50.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370369,1370369}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:03.67,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377544,1383674}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:09.76,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383674,1389764}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:21.77,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389764,1401774}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:33.91,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401774,1413914}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:39.79,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1413914,1419794}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:45.92,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419794,1425924}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:52.01,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1425924,1432014}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:58.10,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432014,1438104}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
